      "factId": "hz.web.c2bcc6b9dce048f0.fact.3",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "For example, Tantek 's home page has (markup simplified) &lt; a href = \"https://github.com/tantek\" rel = \"me\" &gt; @t &lt;/ a &gt; And his GitHub profile itself has (markup simplified) &lt; a href = \"https://tantek.com/\" rel = \"me\" &gt; https://tantek.com/ &lt;/ a &gt; Thus establishing a bi-directional rel-me link and confirming that the two URLs represent the same person.",
